id: TYP-telemetry-state
kind: type
name: Telemetry state
status: draft
description: Snapshot of autopilot state returned by TelemetryListener.get_state(). Fields are populated incrementally as MAVLink messages arrive; absent fields are missing from the dict (not None).
type_kind: record
field: lat: float
field: lon: float
field: alt: float
field: heading: float
field: airspeed: float
field: groundspeed: float
field: mode: int
field: armed: bool
